# LoLDatabaseAPI

LoLDatabaseAPI is a simple and friendly to use API allowing the League of Legends developer community to access to all League of Legend game data in the most convenient way possible.

## Champions [/champions]

**Champion DTO:**

*id(long)*: an identifying key for champions

*lore(string)*: background info on that champion

*championStats(statDTO)*: provides starting stat info on champion

*recommended(List[ItemID])*: provides recommended item build for champion

*gameModes(List[boolean])*: provides a list of gameModes this champion is available on
 



