### Get Specific Champion [GET /champions/{championID}]

*Description: Fetches ChampionDTO for a specific champion.*

+ Parameters
    + championID (string, required)  - champion name in all lower case no spaces


+ Response 200 (application/json)

        "example": {
            "Riven": {
                "id": "1234452134",
                "recommended" : 
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "count": 1,
                            "name": "BoTRK"
                        },
                        {
                            "count": 1,
                            "id": "Duskblade"
                        },
                        {
                            "count": 3,
                            "id": "Potions"
                        }
                    ],
                "championsStats": [
                    "health": 1234,
                    "attackDamage": 341,
                    ...
                ]
                "Lore" : "..."
                "GameModes": {
                    "Normals": true,
                    "Ranked": true,
                    "ARAM": true,
                    "StarGaurdian": false
                }
            }
        }

+ Response 404 (application/json)

        { 
            "error": "Resource not found" 
        }
        
## Items [/items]

**Item DTO**

*frequentlyBuiltOn(List[string])*: List of champions who frequently build this item

*maps(List[boolean])*: List of maps this item is available on

*description(string)*: Description of item stats

*plainText(string)*: Description of this item

*sanitizedDescription(string)*: Description of stat buff and passive

*itemTree(List[strings])*: List of children items required to build this item

*name(string)*: item name/identifier

*id(long)*: item identifier (might make string???)

