## Get Game Mode [/gameModes]
    
**GameModeDTO**

*GameModeID(int)*: key for this game mode (unsure if it will remain int or string)

*mapImg(url)*: a url to image of game mode map

*lore(string)*: lore behind the game mode

*InGameDesciprtion(string)*: description of the in game play for this game mode

*Versions(List[string])*: returns the different types of maps

*PlayableChampions(List[championIDs])*: returns a list of champions you can use on this game mode

*Items(list[ItemID's])*: returns a list of items usable in this game mode

### Get Game Mode Description with Game Mode ID [GET /gameModes/{gameMode}]

*Description: Fetches list of GameModeDTO's for a game mode*


+ Parameter
    + gameMode (number, required) - String game mode all lower case, using dashes instead of space
        1. Summoner's Rift
        2. Howling Abyss
        3. Twisted Treeline
    
+ Response 200 (applicaton/json)
    
        "example": [
            "Summoners Rift": {
                "GameModeID": 1
                "MapImg": "http://url.png"
                "Lore": "will populate with real lore",
                "InGameDescription": "The newest and most...",
                "Versions": [
                    "Summer Version": "It's the first...",
                    "Winter Version": "A variant of the..."
                ],
                "Development": "Summoner Rift evolves...",
                "Playable Champions": [
                    "Lux",
                    "Aatrox",
                    "Caitlyn",
                    "etc."
                ],
                "Items": [
                    "Duskblade",
                    "BoTRK",
                    "etc."
                ]
            }
        ]
        
+ Response 404 (application/json)

        { 
            "error": "Resource not found" 
        }
        
## Summoner's Match History [/summoner/matchHistory]

**MatcheHistoryForSummonerDTO**

*land(string or laneID)*: returns the lane this champion played

*matchID(long)*: unique match id 

*map(mapID)*: mapid of map this match was played on

*gameModeID(gameModeID)*: Game mode identifier

*Items(List[itemID])*: returns a list of items this champion bought in this match



